{"tid":1533763,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人做過brinks押運員","createTime":"2019-09-02T21:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T11:33:17.000Z","uid":88178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9358982e681ebf12b6ceacbdb2038511251fae6b","tid":1533763,"uid":88178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:25:31.000Z","msg":"夜更嘅話好唔好做？見佢係十個鐘一更 比起g4同衛安起碼12碼好 好似幾吸引"},{"pid":"500d4c2b631a963f677d682e4905871ae4fe5f73","tid":1533763,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:26:42.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">堅持下去，團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"b87f3ef9ec48f39364085a12508142dccb008e28","tid":1533763,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/XGsKsXy.gif\" da